[SAY] Help for the dd command. Every command, option, and feature has a help page.
[SAY] Help tags are highlighted. Put your cursor on a tag and press Control right bracket to jump to it.
[SAY] Press Control O to jump back. Just like the jump list.
[SAY] Some help prefixes. Colon H colon command for ex commands. Colon H single quote option single quote for options. Colon H I underscore key for insert mode keys.
[SAY] Vim's help is a superpower. When in doubt, colon help.